1) Controller

Responsible for this app:
Adrian
Contact: adrian_ilka@web.de

2) Data Processing

Lock Screen Timer works without registration and without an account.
We do not collect, store, or process personal data on any server, and we do not transmit your data to us.

Data stored locally on your iPhone (on-device only):

Timer settings (e.g., duration, presets, titles)

App preferences/settings

This data stays on your device and is not shared with third parties.

3) Tracking, Ads, Analytics

Lock Screen Timer uses no tracking, no ads, and no analytics.

4) Internet / Servers

The app does not require an internet connection for its core functionality.
We operate no servers and do not store any user data online.

5) Notifications

If you allow notifications, the app uses them to notify you (for example, when a timer ends).
You can disable notifications at any time in iOS Settings.

6) Third Parties

We do not use third-party SDKs that collect or share personal data.

7) Data Retention

All app data remains on your device until you change/reset it in the app or uninstall the app.

8) Contact

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact: adrian_ilka@web.de
